[/size]Nania is a Redguard (obviously) preset whom I am quite fond of. I spent alot of time on perfecting her, so enjoy!

[size=5][color=purple]Installation[/color]
[/size]
If this is your first preset mod, then unzip the file and place the .jslot file in your \Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets folder. If this folder doesn't exist create it.Â 

[size=4][color=purple]Credits[/color]

[/size]Credits go to the mod authors of the mods I used to create this RaceMenu preset. Go check them out, they do some pretty cool stuff.
